    "remarks_html": "<p>Reports the success or failure of the logon request.</p>\n<p>Possible status codes:</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Status</th>\n<th>Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><code>0x00</code></td>\n<td>Logon accepted, requires proof</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>0x01</code></td>\n<td>Account doesn't exist</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>0x05</code></td>\n<td>Account requires upgrade; see <a href=\"/packet/200/sid-auth-accountupgrade\">C&gt;S 0x57 SID_AUTH_ACCOUNTUPGRADE</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Other</td>\n<td>Unknown (failure)</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>See the <a href=\"/document/24/nls-srp-protocol\">NLS/SRP Protocol</a> document for more information.</p>",
